{"tid":2194954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水雞嶺迴旋處案 博文老師發起眾籌","createTime":"2020-09-09T00:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T16:56:29.000Z","uid":2785,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7f224a51e1dc626b06dadd763a365c02e3ec8fc5","tid":2194954,"uid":2785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T00:33:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CE4Z6tEAmI8/?igshid=n1q9w31mntgu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCE4Z6tEAmI8%2F%3Figshid%3Dn1q9w31mntgu&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNVe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=2efa3e7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCE4Z6tEAmI8%2F%3Figshid%3Dn1q9w31mntgu&h=9cc6d198\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CE4Z6tEAmI8/?igshid=n1q9w31mntgu</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HPnj2RA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHPnj2RA.jpg&h=8859e242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信依單案 無一個覺得佢唔係冤枉 但正正佢就係慘被判上牢獄之苦<br />\n<br />\n前蘇聯離心份子作家、諾貝爾獎得主索忍尼辛的一段話：<br />\n「我們知道他們在說謊，他們也知道自己是說謊，他們也知道我們知道他們在說謊，我們也知道他們知道我們知道他們說謊，但是他們依然在說謊」。<br />\n<br />\n希望起碼令佢唔洗擔心屋企人 擔心樣野<br />\n請幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n在此希望博文老師可以沉冤得雪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc21d1a9856598075dd3ad0a0941977f54e34a7","tid":2194954,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T00:33:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ebb21e7c2575d4a148fa40fce165b1ce67a30c0","tid":2194954,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f